It Is Here and We Need to Help Stop It: Human Trafficking
Youth and young adults are so targeted, there was absolutely nothing in regards to communication, education, or protection that was available to arm them with awareness

data.description: With the social media handle Jenn at WAR, community educator Jenn Amo is on a mission against human trafficking.
data.title: ‘It Is Here and We Need to Help Stop It’: Human Trafficking
